      "review_title": "Level 2",
      "review_description": "I can’t get past level 2 because some of the flames and smoke won’t go out no matter how much water or fire extinguisher I used.\nSo I couldn’t save most of the people.\nThe idea is really cool. Also there could be more mass behind the axes.\nAre there a way I could email you gameplay . Because I really don’t know how to use discord.  But with the furniture . Won’t brake like the sofa. It doesn’t even show the hit indicator flashing. And there’s flames on the back wall. The flames go out but not the smoke itself.",
